<Base
  title="Fresh Pantry — your kitchen, remembered"
  description="Fresh Pantry tracks what's in your fridge, freezer, and pantry, flags what's about to expire, and suggests recipes from what you already have."
>
  <nav><a href="/">← Sunpebble</a></nav>
  <h1>Fresh Pantry</h1>
  <p class="tagline">Your kitchen, remembered. Track what's in the fridge and cook it before it expires.</p>

  <ul class="features">
    <li><strong>Every shelf, one inventory</strong>
        <span>Fridge, freezer, and pantry in a single list, with quantities that stay honest.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Expiry at a glance</strong>
        <span>Fresh, expiring soon, or expired — a quiet color and a label, never an alarm.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Cook from what you have</strong>
        <span>Recipes matched against your actual stock, so tonight's dinner uses what's expiring first.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Paste, review, done</strong>
        <span>Paste a shopping receipt or a list; Fresh Pantry proposes the updates and you confirm before anything changes.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Share the pantry</strong>
        <span>Everyone in your household sees the same shelves, the same shopping list.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Works offline</strong>
        <span>Local-first: the app is fully usable without a connection and syncs quietly when you're back.</span></li>
  </ul>

  <span class="badge">Coming soon to the App Store</span>

